{"tid":415753,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓奴請入 新貓入屋問題","createTime":"2017-09-27T08:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T03:53:45.000Z","uid":113589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d65878c740539f821c39ca313fabfae1bb291128","tid":415753,"uid":113589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"舊貓3個月大 住左屋企1個月<br />\n早幾日帶隻新貓番去（2個月大）<br />\n頭一兩日 舊貓見到新貓都會有惡意地fee佢<br />\n之後見到舊貓成日係個籠出邊想撩新貓玩<br />\n<br />\n跟住開始俾佢地一齊出嚟行吓<br />\n之後見到狗貓冇再fee佢<br />\n有時仲打埋一舊（多數都係舊貓攬住新貓）<br />\n但係我唔知佢哋係玩定打架<br />\n<br />\n 聽到新貓係咁慘叫 但有時有見到舊貓打打下幫佢舔毛<br />\n新貓又不停逃走 但有時又追番轉頭<br />\n<br />\n都唔知佢哋係咪打架定玩<br />\n求救"},{"pid":"4c992e4d2bc4b86c798212688ca7d204a924f054","tid":415753,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"係舊貓（老大）調教新人咁樣<br />\n會lam新貓代表接受咗佢"},{"pid":"87aa6a7b329d767992f6f9a0242dbaece6d5b572","tid":415753,"uid":113589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係舊貓（老大）調教新人咁樣<br />\n會lam新貓代表接受咗佢</blockquote><br />\n但係獲獲新貓都叫得好慘<br />\n見到佢只係舔佢一兩下<br />\n但咬佢嘅時間比較多"},{"pid":"db70a7b02b74f387bdc03a0036017aafd09587a2","tid":415753,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係舊貓（老大）調教新人咁樣<br />\n會lam新貓代表接受咗佢</blockquote><br />\n但係獲獲新貓都叫得好慘<br />\n見到佢只係舔佢一兩下<br />\n但咬佢嘅時間比較多</blockquote><br />\n其實只要舊貓無再fee佢就無事<br />\n因為佢想新貓融入依個環境<br />\n教導佢依度邊個係大佬<br />\n係叫得慘d，但無流血就ok <br />\n如果萬一真係見到唔對路<br />\n就將兩隻分開 一個困房一個困其他地方<br />\n唔好畀佢地見到大家幾小時<br />\n再放返出黎"},{"pid":"89f962cb13c2c6d6ebc374938ffec0fa12a0f722","tid":415753,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"無再fee已經代表接受左成<br />\n<br />\n通常打交係純粹想「下馬威」，「撩下你」"},{"pid":"44b9780783cc7d2118a231a15fb4a4fdce2e868e","tid":415753,"uid":113589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:22:10.000Z","msg":"即係舊貓有lam新貓即係ok?"},{"pid":"517b0cc2c30a012d5b5fd426065bec2975b1a7f8","tid":415753,"uid":99840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係舊貓有lam新貓即係ok?</blockquote><br />\n非常OK"},{"pid":"d4cf073f7e79ad61c73dfa30fe095783a230b7f3","tid":415753,"uid":113589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:43:34.000Z","msg":"但獲獲都隻新貓喪慘叫 有d擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為體型差少少<br />\n新貓有時又有想推開佢同逃走"},{"pid":"fd84ab2f32d0c64241c7aefe6017564bf87b0571","tid":415753,"uid":13775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"有無相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00e46223a335f0e234d57bbafa81042f5d3d92b","tid":415753,"uid":48276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但獲獲都隻新貓喪慘叫 有d擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為體型差少少<br />\n新貓有時又有想推開佢同逃走</blockquote><br />\n真係驚既<br />\n咪新貓入籠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de453ecaeb29b75609ec4ef8701aa3873a8d3cd","tid":415753,"uid":144695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"新貓有冇撩舊貓？<br />\n我屋企個兩隻又係咁，舊貓咬到新貓慘叫<br />\n舊貓體重係新貓兩倍<br />\n但係新貓成日沖去撩舊貓先，<br />\n不過其實冇流血都唔洗理，<br />\n反而新貓唔夠打但有時咬到舊貓甩毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a5d074fe3b13d41d13e560fffee7fec3d67fd5","tid":415753,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"歲數太接近，最理想係製造一啲新貓入到而舊貓入唔到嘅位，等新貓體力不繼都有位匿埋<br />\n<br />\n現階段無咩可以做，由佢哋打"},{"pid":"dc28860317498bbbda3895562f5d26fe9689acae","tid":415753,"uid":98779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"無fee就成功啦，一時打架一時lam毛係正常。<br />\n如果打到慘叫就分開佢地就得。<br />\n<br />\n2隻貓走黎走去好有生氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c55b21cebbf94dd39cf55836a71778f6e5dae04","tid":415753,"uid":113589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ny[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003720_73911974d86f9bb1fbacaea2a2f2fcbe.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003720_73911974d86f9bb1fbacaea2a2f2fcbe.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=1Bsysqd9aMMxOoQO0Q2moCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a5d08c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003720_73911974d86f9bb1fbacaea2a2f2fcbe.jpg[/img</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003720_7084b55a843bad78591a72639ec192dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003720_7084b55a843bad78591a72639ec192dd.jpg&h=661ff55f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13070cdcd3978a33fb537c7711fea2023888f7b1","tid":415753,"uid":113589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003807_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003807_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg&h=f90727d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003808_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003808_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg&h=218a4278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003808_dba7d951ab58e4f4fc3ecf1ce3713f61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003808_dba7d951ab58e4f4fc3ecf1ce3713f61.jpg&h=e9a7659e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4a77dc330af380e425601a0f89e3a4288353c34","tid":415753,"uid":74162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003807_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003807_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg&h=f90727d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003808_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003808_c418bfa2d81e207b8769c30544987df4.jpg&h=218a4278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/003808_dba7d951ab58e4f4fc3ecf1ce3713f61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F003808_dba7d951ab58e4f4fc3ecf1ce3713f61.jpg&h=e9a7659e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好cute"},{"pid":"8d2d0c009c7c089dc0a28819a446c2a0569f8e04","tid":415753,"uid":47433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:18:28.000Z","msg":"兩隻bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48529f9ab11b6437856bfbd34037e37ee34bd434","tid":415753,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"我已經由好擔心到放棄了<br />\n由得佢地打 冇傷冇出血就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054bb5a033de13c09805657b6db71f94f8f6e5e8","tid":415753,"uid":17408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"就咁睇就似玩啦 成個肚仔反曬出黎 證明冇咩問題<br />\n驚就多啲剪指甲 廢事太尖 整傷"}]}